OL,3,C'It's not welfare or warfare': Ex
OL,4,Carmed forces minister on defence
OL,5,Cspending
OL,7,FThe former armed forces minister has
OL,8,Fsaid it should not be a choice between
OL,9,F"welfare or warfare", when it comes to
OL,10,Fdecision-making around defence
OL,11,Finvestment.
OL,13,FSpeaking to Good Morning Britain on
OL,14,FFriday, Al Carns said the government
OL,15,Fneeds to "be innovative to find the
OL,16,Fmoney to put into the defence
OL,17,Findustry".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
