OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781387267
OL,3,C'It's not welfare or warfare': Ex
OL,4,Carmed forces minister on defence
OL,5,Cspending
OL,7,FCarns resigned on Thursday night
OL,8,Ffollowing the surprise departure of
OL,9,FJohn Healey, who quit as defence
OL,10,Fsecretary over a disagreement about
OL,11,Fmilitary spending.
OL,13,FHealey accused Prime Minister Keir
OL,14,FStarmer of making the country "less
OL,15,Fsafe".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781387267
OL,3,C'It's not welfare or warfare': Ex
OL,4,Carmed forces minister on defence
OL,5,Cspending
OL,7,FCarns, whose resignation followed a
OL,8,Ffew hours later, said: "We need to
OL,9,Fgive out armed forces the kit and
OL,10,Fequipment that they require" and said
OL,11,Fthat the Defence Investment Plan (DIP)
OL,12,Fwas not enough.
OL,14,FThe investment plan was largely viewed
OL,15,Fas a legacy project for the prime
OL,16,Fminister, who was due to appear in
OL,17,FSwindon on Friday to launch the long
OL,18,Fawaited DIP.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781387267
OL,3,C'It's not welfare or warfare': Ex
OL,4,Carmed forces minister on defence
OL,5,Cspending
OL,7,FCarns told ITV that "Number 10 must be
OL,8,Fmore flexible with how it finds the
OL,9,Fmoney" and suggested further borrowing
OL,10,Fas an option.
OL,12,FHe went on to say that the government
OL,13,Fhas not "learned lessons from Ukraine".
OL,15,FDefending the government, Business
OL,16,FSecretary Peter Kyle told ITV News
OL,17,Fthat they were "investing historic
OL,18,Famounts of money" but said they must
OL,19,F"get it right".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
