FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781387267
OL,3,C'It's not welfare or warfare': Ex
OL,4,Carmed forces minister on defence
OL,5,Cspending
OL,7,FKyle added: "we need to get a grip on
OL,8,Fpublic finances and invest in growth"
OL,9,Fand said the DIP will be announced
OL,10,Fbefore the NATO summit at the start of
OL,11,FJuly.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FDan Jarvis has now been appointed as
OL,19,Fthe new Defence Secretary, stepping up
OL,20,Ffrom his position as Security minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
