PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1781387267
OL,3,C'It's not welfare or warfare': Ex
OL,4,Carmed forces minister on defence
OL,5,Cspending
OL,7,FIn a statement Starmer said he was
OL,8,Fpleased to make the appointment, at a
OL,9,Ftime when the government was working
OL,10,Fto "meet the growing threats facing
OL,11,Four country".
OL,13,FHe wrote: "My first duty is to keep
OL,14,Fthe British people safe, and I will
OL,15,Falways do what is necessary to protect
OL,16,Four national security."
OL,18,FKyle said Jarvis has "a great history
OL,19,Fof service".
OL,26,@rD@DOUuD@KOU
