OL,3,C'It's not welfare or warfare': Ex
OL,4,Carmed forces minister on defence
OL,5,Cspending
OL,7,FCarns said that the new defence
OL,8,Fsecterary was "an exceptionally well
OL,9,Frespected man, he will steady the
OL,10,Fship, he will do well".
OL,12,FThe former armed forces minister has
OL,13,Fnot ruled out a potential bid for the
OL,14,FLabour leadership, with mounting
OL,15,Fpressure on the PM.
OL,17,FCarns said he hadn't receieved his P45
OL,18,Ffrom the last job and said "we'll see
OL,19,Fwhat happens in the future".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
